sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Augmented Citizen
  participant Portal as Reality.OS Portal
  participant Cozo as CozoDB Local
  participant SC as SovereigntyCore
  participant ALN as ALN Mainnet

  User->>Portal: Click "BCI Calibration"
  Portal->>Cozo: Query channel status
  Cozo-->>Portal: Return channel data
  Portal->>SC: Request corridor evaluation
  SC->>SC: Check RoH envelopes
  SC-->>Portal: Approval granted
  Portal->>SC: Submit calibration request
  SC->>ALN: Anchor to ROW ledger
  ALN-->>SC: Return transaction hash
  SC->>Cozo: Store in transaction table
  Cozo-->>Portal: Confirmation
  Portal->>User: Display success
